    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/ae66dd8761007c92b3df8fbe4745b541.avif?t=1734092884\" width=640 height=384 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farkas: the Last Redhaft</strong> 是一款剧情丰富的rogue-like游戏，融入了RPG机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/0c8764ef13db188069045179fd69f5b0.poster.avif?t=1734092884\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/0c8764ef13db188069045179fd69f5b0.webm?t=1734092884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的祖先之地遭到占领，所有的责任都落在了你的肩上！奉国王之命，你向南出发，试图终结哥布林的入侵，但那些曾经熟悉的道路，如今变得陌生且危机四伏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 在战斗中创造属于你自己的道路！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会优先选择哪条路径？猫、熊、剑士，还是山羊？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/245cde94e7b849e3abd2ee693ec8ab84.avif?t=1734092884\" width=422 height=292 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用最猛烈的终结技击败敌人！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过独特的动画和快速的战斗机制，与敌人共舞！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/2bbb5ce09b22abb7e7817edbf1446eee.apng?t=1734092884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389660/extras/2bbb5ce09b22abb7e7817edbf1446eee.poster.avif?t=1734092884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=639 height=213 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> 用美丽的手绘像素艺术探索赫斯佩里亚</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> 支持手柄操作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> 通过采矿和收集升级你的装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> 超过10场Boss战斗和30种不同的敌人</p>",
